{"tid":1375863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成立冷氣軍師參謀團","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:03:03.000Z","uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"367dc387621438d39323147733072a4726e4c2c1","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"其實如果可以多d人做呢樣嘢應該幾好<br />\n各大channel 已經有曬情報<br />\n只係冇人整合<br />\n例如收集情報整合完<br />\n係地圖到講邊到有狗<br />\n邊到重軍駐守<br />\n邊到推進緊<br />\n等前線又好<br />\n物資又好<br />\n和理非又好<br />\n清楚知道成個場嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n本channel 只為提供情報<br />\n所有行動現場决定<br />\n本channel 亦會關閉討論功能<br />\n有意成為冷氣軍師可pm我申請做admit <br />\n本人用tg時日尚短<br />\n任何私隱安全問題可提出<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做 <br />\n不割席 不督灰 不指責<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/indoorstaffofficergroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Findoorstaffofficergroup&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=fef744d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/indoorstaffofficergroup</a>"},{"pid":"008b46bf9cdac8a92a7e03f0a21e120056167da7","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c12284659cb0779e7750fd9ff6464c622602cd2","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c38ee263ab9ba31a628a262bc06fa158096895d","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c12284659cb0779e7750fd9ff6464c622602cd2","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1588a31199c659ce75a1f0d8f2c4c0cb391b477c","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb9c20d39a0c373809e5ff57abb28c5d8ad71a6","tid":1375863,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor